{"tid":1940922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"7婆：願聽業界意見 最極端包括關閉餐廳控制營業時間","createTime":"2020-03-24T06:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T11:43:41.000Z","uid":216992,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"648f7c2c46e58bd42a61b5437312ef8afbd21704","tid":1940922,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"政府將會制訂法例，暫時禁止領有酒牌的食肆、酒吧和會社，出售或供應酒類飲品，以進一步推動減少社交接觸。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥說，需要數日深入研究法律工作，願意聽取業界意見，最極端手段包括關閉餐廳以及控制營業時間等。　<br />\n<br />\n她又對有人公然違反強制家居檢疫令表示失望同痛心，認為不值得為了出一次街，而面對還柙和留下刑事紀錄。"},{"pid":"8639ebc3ea272d49487714544ba63ddca8df2d99","tid":1940922,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516458-20200324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516458-20200324.htm&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=bbdd4071\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516458-20200324.htm&h=ad3d061e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516458-20200324.htm</a>"},{"pid":"591d16810b534c6aee7b585c625e97a64c4f2b38","tid":1940922,"uid":216992,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />願聽意見 但而家先封關 仲要照比大陸人入"},{"pid":"f9f35bd610be7749e65a9ced46f8e0f3864eeed2","tid":1940922,"uid":216992,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:02:57.000Z","msg":"係咪會再有一次搶購潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c640c9562a3b7bfbcef183cbd4ac419f8ba086","tid":1940922,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"柒婆: 願意聽意見 但要控制住你"},{"pid":"5564ff5f13ffde5f